**Week4**
     In Beijing, there is an interesting food transit way. As we know, some restaurant offer food delivering services, but what if you want to order a meal from a restaurant which doesn’t supply this service? Never mind if you live in Beijing. You may order any restaurant and use an app to tell the rider to get it for you, then get the meal when he arrived your front door with an extra little fee. Because of Beijing’s serious traffic problems, most people would rather stay home then go out for food, so food delivering jobs get popular in a short time. This way of transport not only saved tons of time and also decreases global warming, because the deliver riders only ride electric motors, since Beijing haven’t release any gasoline motor licenses for decades, they truly helped decreasing the temperature of Earth.
     
